### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3076
@tenantId = 523789bc-67a6-11f1-8237-00505661e513
@apiKey = your-api-key-here
@hostname = localhost
@emailCode = em_abc123def456

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# GET /logs/:tenantId/email  —  List email log
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all emails (default page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs/{{tenantId}}/email
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}

###

### List emails — page 2 with 25 per page
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs/{{tenantId}}/email?page=2&pageSize=25
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}

###

### Filter by status: sent
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs/{{tenantId}}/email?status=sent
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}

###

### Filter by status: failed
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs/{{tenantId}}/email?status=failed
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}

###

### Filter by status: queued
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs/{{tenantId}}/email?status=queued
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}

###

### Filter by template code
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs/{{tenantId}}/email?templateCode=welcome-email
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}

###

### Filter by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs/{{tenantId}}/email?fromDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00Z&toDate=2026-06-14T23:59:59Z
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}

###

### Combined filter — failed emails from a specific template this month
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs/{{tenantId}}/email?status=failed&templateCode=invoice-template&fromDate=2026-06-01T00:00:00Z&pageSize=50
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# GET /logs/:tenantId/email/:emailCode  —  Email details
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Get full details for a single email
GET {{baseUrl}}/logs/{{tenantId}}/email/{{emailCode}}
X-Tenant-ID: {{tenantId}}
X-APIKEY: {{apiKey}}
X-Hostname: {{hostname}}

###
